text: Vrancea () is a county (judeţ) in Romania. The capital of Vrancea County is Focşani. It is mostly in the historical region of Moldavia. The southern part of Vrancea County is not in Moldavia. ==Demographics== About 387,630 people were living in Vrancea County as of the year 2002.
